				<td width="207"><a href="details.html"><img height="150" width="200" src="ai3link0010s.gif" lowsrc="ai3link0010sls.gif" border="0"></a></td>
				<td valign="top">
					<p class="size1">The AI3 testbed network is a part of global/international Internet infrastructure based on satellite communication system in Asian region. This network provides Internet direct connection among AI3 partners.</p>
					<p>Its backbone part consists of an uni-directional link, point-to-point links based on Ku-band/C-band satellite communication channels and high-speed ATM connection between 2 hub stations in Japan.</p>
					<p class="size1">The detail for the map of our testbed network is available when you <a href="details.html">click the left figure</a>.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<br>
		<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="655">
			<tr>
				<td width="655">
					<div align="left">
						An uni-directional Ku-band link is ready and its bandwidth is 2Mbps from Japan to Asian countries. All the p2p links are in asymmetric configuration: 1.5Mbps from Japan and 512kbps to Japan. Between 2 hub stations, 10Mbps ATM link is currently installed.</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
